media:group.media:title: Pratt Blueprint: September 2022 Edition
media:group.media:description:
Dean Jerome Lynch welcomes the Duke Engineering community to the September 2022 edition of "Pratt Blueprint," a monthly newsletter curated with purpose: to provide high-impact information about our community in a useful and digestible format.
